{"tid":2187560,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"GeForce RTX 30 新卡可能出現嚴重炒價","createTime":"2020-09-03T16:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T06:21:06.000Z","uid":135488,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1f1a5f340a1e8cbbbbf759f343eff8b93b514e","tid":2187560,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19707/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F_8nm_%E5%88%B6%E7%A8%8B__GPU_%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8_GeForce_RTX_30_%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%82%92%E5%83%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19707%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2598%259F_8nm_%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25A8%258B__GPU_%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A8_GeForce_RTX_30_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%2583%25B9&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=2c159acb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19707/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F_8nm_%E5%88%B6%E7%A8%8B__GPU_%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8_GeForce_RTX_30_%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%A1%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%82%92%E5%83%B9</a><br />\n為何選三星 8nm 制程 ? GPU 非常缺貨<br />\n<br />\nGeForce RTX 30 新卡可能出現嚴重炒價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA 正式發佈新一代 RTX 30 新卡，驚人的性價比為顯示卡市場帶來了重大衝撃，在未發佈前傳統是使用 TSMC 7nm 制程，但為何最後變成了 SAMSUNG 8nm 呢 ? 有台灣卡廠表示 GeForce RTX 30 GPU 供貨到今年底前仍會相當候貨，意味著雖然 NVIDIA 官方建議售價雖然偏低，但實際上市場售價可能會出現嚴重炒價。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n原本外界均影為 NVIDIA 新一代 GA102 / GA104 GPU 會與運算用的 A100 GPU 一樣採用 TSMC 7nm 制程，結果爆大冷是特別為 NVIDIA 研發的 SAMSUNG 8nm 制程，雖然數字上好像沒差多少，但實際上 SAMSUNG 其實是由 10nm 制程改良而生，與 TSMC 7nm 制程在技術差了一代。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n首先從電晶體密度來說，TSMC 7nm的密度大約是每毫米擁有 9,600 萬個電晶體，SAMSUNG 8nm 每毫米擁有 6,100 萬個電晶體，兩者相差了 40%，光是 GPU 晶片面積就有很大差距，幸好是新制程仍能保持 1.7GHz 時脈。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n8nm<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據台灣顯示卡廠業者指出，NVIDIA選擇 SAMSUNG 8nm 制程主要是成本的考量，TSMC 7nm 制程 12 吋晶圓代工報價不低於 8000~10000美元，相信 SAMSUNG 8nm 作為一種的制程，晶片代工差價至少有 30%，這也是 RTX 30 系列顯示卡售價能能降低的重要因素。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n雖然 GPU 代工價格能壓低但產能卻非常緊張，直至今年底前供充都會處於緊張狀態，意味著雖然 NVIDIA 官方建議售價雖然偏低，但實際上市場售價可能會出現嚴重炒價，對於香港用家來說初上市美金價 10  算、12 算也已經習以為常。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nRTX 30"},{"pid":"825cb968e862347d460879dae760cec1a6d21364","tid":2187560,"uid":353358,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"無興趣急買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有排用唔盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2080Ti開心使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6f46b692a724531ccf9ac1e7c13a167207dbc0","tid":2187560,"uid":119080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"係唔撚係啊<br />\n又流出3070ti 16gb版<br />\n又要放風焗住人搶"},{"pid":"546efd8f51ed26aeca4a647d9a824ce0fa7f9be1","tid":2187560,"uid":135488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"825cb968e862347d460879dae760cec1a6d21364","tid":2187560,"uid":353358,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"無興趣急買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有排用唔盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2080Ti開心使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"我張癲佬3d 2080ti<br />\n上個月賣咗7k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇後備卡"},{"pid":"c3943d88ab42d39d5cb5c087787ef4d82169b318","tid":2187560,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825cb968e862347d460879dae760cec1a6d21364","tid":2187560,"uid":353358,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:3